Tiles.Title: German Darts Open - Day 1 Session 2
Tiles.Description: All the action from Jena's Sparkassen-Arena, as the opening day of the 2022 German Darts Open continues. The event sees 48 of the world's best talent go head-to-head, with a $29,000 prize on offer to the winner.
Tiles.Label: German Darts Open

Tiles.Title: Wagner vs. Sanchez: Fight Night
Tiles.Description: ​Canadian puncher Josh 'The Boss' Wagner (12-0) is out to impress, enjoying a main event clash against Mexico's Jorge Sanchez (13-2). Enjoy a fantastic night of boxing, as the fighting pride of Edmonton seeks to remain undefeated.
Tiles.Label: Wagner vs. Sanchez

Tiles.Title: Atletico Madrid vs. Real Sociedad
Tiles.Description: Amaiur Sarriegi netted in both fixtures for Real Sociedad against Atletico Madrid last season, on route to scoring 17 goals in the league. Can she do it again, or will the Atletico defense stand tall against her?
Tiles.Label: Liga F

Tiles.Title: Drone Champions League - Lake Zurich Race
Tiles.Description: After a summer hiatus, the Drone Champions League makes its return at the 2022 Lake Zurich Championship. Catch all the action from Switzerland, as the world's best virtual pilots compete in one of Europe's most challenging and unique locations.
Tiles.Label: Drone Champions League

Tiles.Title: German Darts Open - Day 2 Session 1
Tiles.Description: Join us inside Jena's Sparkassen Arena, as the second day of the 2022 German Darts Open gets underway. Michael van Gerwen is the reigning champion, following an 8-3 victory over England's Ian White in the 2019 final showpiece.
Tiles.Label: German Darts Open

Tiles.Title: Villarreal vs. Real Madrid
Tiles.Description: Real Madrid starts its domestic league season with an away day at Ciudad Deportiva to play Villarreal. Esther Gonzalez is a critical part of the Real squad, having already scored four goals in continental competition.
Tiles.Label: Liga F

Tiles.Title: German Darts Open - Day 2 Session 2
Tiles.Description: Join us inside Jena's Sparkassen Arena, as the second day of the 2022 German Darts Open continues. Michael van Gerwen is the reigning champion, following an 8-3 victory over England's Ian White in the 2019 final showpiece.
Tiles.Label: German Darts Open

Tiles.Title: Singh vs. Vrenozi - Fight Night
Tiles.Description: Indian puncher Sukhdeep Singh (12-0) is out to make a statement, facing Albania's Xhuljo Vrenozi (18-4) in Brampton, Canada. This featured middleweight bout is certain to impress, with Singh seeking to remain undefeated as a professional.
Tiles.Label: Bhatti vs. Vrenozi

Tiles.Title: German Darts Open - Day 3 Session 1
Tiles.Description: The German Open heads into its final day, with the third round of action taking place in this afternoon's session. The last two World Champions, Peter Wright and Gerwyn Price, both sit on this side of the draw, and could meet in the quarter-finals.
Tiles.Label: German Darts Open

Tiles.Title: Red Bull Hardline UK
Tiles.Description: The world's best downhill mountain bikers head to Machynlleth to navigate huge jumps, boulder drops and unpredictable weather.
Tiles.Label: Red Bull TV

Tiles.Title: German Darts Open - Day 3 Session 2
Tiles.Description: It's crunch time at the German Darts Open as the winner will be crowned from the eight remaining players in the competition. Jonny Clayton has seemingly not dropped off at all in the last two years, and will want to add to his trophy haul here.
Tiles.Label: German Darts Open

Tiles.Title: Red Bull Cliff Diving World Series Sisikon
Tiles.Description: The Red Bull Cliff Diving World Series heads for Switzerland where Rhiannan Iffland will be looking to emerge victorious and win at each of the 18 locations she has competed at.
Tiles.Label: Red Bull TV

Tiles.Title: Canelo vs. GGG III - DAZN Boxing Show Live and Press Conference
Tiles.Description: Prepare for a historic trilogy, as Canelo Alvarez and Gennady Golovkin come face-to-face at the pre-fight press conference. The two officially collide on September 17 in Las Vegas, where the undisputed super-middleweight championship is at stake.
Tiles.Label: Canelo vs. GGG III

Tiles.Title: Harvest Farms - Day 1
Tiles.Description: Tune into all the action from the Harvest Farms golf course in Chicago as the first day tees off with the likes of Dustin Johnson, Bryson DeChambeau, and Phil Mickelson all participating.
Tiles.Label: LIV Golf Invitational Series

Tiles.Title: Canelo vs. GGG III - DAZN Boxing Show Live and Weigh-In
Tiles.Description: Canelo Alvarez and Gennady Golovkin tip the scales, ahead of their undisputed super-middleweight trilogy in Las Vegas. Follow all of the live action with the DAZN Boxing Show team, as we look forward to a history-making showdown in Sin City.
Tiles.Label: Canelo vs. GGG III

Tiles.Title: Harvest Farms - Day 2
Tiles.Description: It’s time for the second day of golfing wonder here at Harvest Farms in Chicago, as part of the LIV Golf series. Cameron Smith, Sergio Garcia, and Kevin Na are all expected to make an appearance in this exciting competition.
Tiles.Label: LIV Golf Invitational Series

Tiles.Title: The DAZN Boxing Show Live - Canelo vs. GGG III
Tiles.Description: Get the ultimate preview, as we build up to a huge clash in Las Vegas between Canelo Alvarez and Gennady Golovkin. Join our panel of experts live from Sin City, as two of the world's best prepare to dance under the lights for the third time
Tiles.Label: Canelo vs. GGG III

Tiles.Title: Canelo vs. GGG III: Fight Night
Tiles.Description: The wait is officially over. Saul 'Canelo' Alvarez and Gennadiy Golovkin clash in a much-awaited trilogy in Las Vegas. After a draw in their first bout and Canelo's narrow win in the second, the pair hope to settle one of boxing's biggest rivalries.
Tiles.Label: Canelo vs. GGG III

Tiles.Title: Harvest Farms - Day 3
Tiles.Description: Be sure to follow the dramatic conclusion of the weekend here at Harvest Farms in Chicago. Dustin Johnson won the last event in Boston, can he do it all over again in front of another American crowd?
Tiles.Label: LIV Golf Invitational Series

Tiles.Title: Wood vs. Lara: Fight Night
Tiles.Description: After defending his WBA featherweight title against Michael Conlan, Leigh Wood now sets his sights on Mexican fighter, Mauricio Lara. Can Wood deliver yet another enthralling fight for his home crowd in Nottingham?
Tiles.Label: Wood vs. Lara

Tiles.Title: Eubank Jr. vs. Benn: Fight Night
Tiles.Description: In a grudge match over 30 years in the making, Chris Eubank Jr. and Conor Benn will pick up where their fathers left off when the two Brits go head-to-head in a huge matchup on October 8.
Tiles.Label: Eubank Jr. vs. Benn

Tiles.Title: Bivol vs. Ramirez: Fight Night
Tiles.Description: ​A title opportunity has arisen for Gilberto Ramirez (44-0), who makes his ring return against WBA light-heavyweight king Dmitry Bivol (20-0). The bout marks another mandatory defence for Bivol, who is fresh from an upset victory over Canelo Alvarez.
Tiles.Label: Bivol vs. Ramirez

Tiles.Title: Love vs. Spark: Fight Night
Tiles.Description: Montana Love (18-0-1) headlines his hometown of Cleveland for the first time, as he collides with Australian puncher Steve Spark (15-2). Love will hope to defend his IBF North American super-lightweight title, after he claimed the strap back in May.
Tiles.Label: Love vs. Spark
